location.fullValue: The Seneca Plan, The Village at Cabin Branch

data.description: Explore this beautiful Brick-front townhome facing greenspace, located in the Cabin Branch community in Clarksburg. This is one of the larger models featuring 3 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a spacious 2,500 sq ft of living space, all in impeccable condition. This home is better-than-brand new with a ton of builder and custom upgrades by caring homeowners! As you enter, you'll be greeted by gleaming hardwood flooring, an open floorplan main level with an abundance of natural sunlight!  There is a living room that opens to a chef’s kitchen featuring a 7ft island with Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas cooktop and hood, and a comfortable area for dining. The open concept floor plan is complemented by high ceilings, and smart home features. There is a powder room and the kitchen opens to an expansive deck with Trex decking and vinyl railing. Upstairs, you'll find 3 bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with recessed lighting a beautifully appointed primary shower with bench seating. The lower level is finished with a cozy family room and an attached full bath. The 2-car garage is converted to a den with additional insulation, custom doors and air handler – you have to see it to believe it! Built in 2021, this townhome looks and feels brand new, with the original owner having barely lived in it. The community itself offers amenities such as a clubhouse, playgrounds, pools, and scenic walking/jogging paths. Conveniently located a stone's throw away from the Premium Outlets and with easy access to I-270, this property is a must-see. Schedule your showing today to experience the comfort and elegance of this meticulously maintained home!
